"	NOP Arrow keys - All Mode
noremap <Up> <NOP>
noremap <Down> <NOP>
noremap <Left> <NOP>
noremap <Right> <NOP>

"	NOP Home|End Keys - All Modes
noremap <Home> <NOP>
noremap <End> <NOP>

"	NOP Backspace in Command Mode
cnoremap <Backspace> <NOP>
